longBusinessSummary: JLT Mobile Computers AB (publ) produces and sells rugged computing solutions in the Nordic countries, the rest of Europe, the Middle East, Africa, the Americas, and internationally. The company offers vehicle-mount computers; rugged tablets and handheld devices; accessories, such as barcode scanners, mounts, keyboards and stylus, antennas and antenna connectors, power supply and cables, and ingress protection and screen protectors; software solutions; and Winmate, which includes enterprise mobility, industrial panel PCs, and HMIs. It provides customized rugged computers and custom-made devices, including antennas, cables and mounting, GPS boards and connectors, and CAN-bus. The company sells its products through a network of resellers and system integrators to various industries, including warehousing and distribution, agriculture, manufacturing, mining, ports, and transportation. JLT Mobile Computers AB (publ) was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Växjö, Sweden.
